{"word":"λαγών","slug":"λαγών","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λαγών</b></el> <el>(λᾰγών, όνος,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:λαγαρός'><el>λαγαρός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>the hollow on each side below the ribs, the flank</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>the flanks</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>any hollow</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}